node.name: CompassApp
node.description: The goal of this project was to create an app that can be used as a sort of waypoint detection. The user will set a waypoint(GPS Coordinates)at their location and be free to move around our "Compass" will always point you in the right direction to the waypoint you set. Multiple waypoints can be set in the app.
